{"tid":1165859,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[ICAC] 廉政專員白韞六支持修訂《逃犯條例》避免香港成為逃犯天堂","createTime":"2019-05-22T05:20:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T05:37:47.000Z","uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"843b8653933b021e8530de080fa254c9c23720e7","tid":1165859,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:20:04.000Z","msg":"<strong>【逃犯條例】白韞六支持修例 稱能堵塞漏洞 免港成避罪天堂</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/bak6-icac_O4mqw_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fbak6-icac_O4mqw_1200x0.png&h=5a5c064f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廉政公署第七屆國際會議今早在灣仔會展舉行，廉政專員白韞六會見傳媒時表明支持修訂《逃犯條例》，又稱修例可以堵塞制度漏洞，避免香港成為逃犯的避罪天堂。<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥、律政司司長鄭若驊、終審法院首席法官馬道立及廉政專員白韞六等人，今早出席廉政公署第七屆國際會議開幕禮。被問及對港府修訂《逃犯條例》看法時，白韞六表示，廉署是一個執法機構，有責任執法維護法治和治安，若本港法例有漏洞，希望透過修例堵塞。<br />\n<br />\n白韞六又指，知道有一些干犯貪污罪行的人士在海外犯罪後藏身香港，但他不掌握這類匿藏人士的實際數字。白韞六認為，通過修例不會影響香港和其他國家合作打擊貪污的工作。<br />\n<br />\n白韞六在會上致歡迎辭時表示，香港視廉潔及法治為極度重要的基本價值，是香港繼續成為國際大都市的基石。他又表示，貪污罪行性質日益變得跨國，廉署一直促進國際合作，打擊貪污罪行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E7%99%BD%E9%9F%9E%E5%85%AD%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B-%E7%A8%B1%E8%83%BD%E5%A0%B5%E5%A1%9E%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E-%E5%85%8D%E6%B8%AF%E6%88%90%E9%81%BF%E7%BD%AA%E5%A4%A9%E5%A0%82/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E7%2599%25BD%25E9%259F%259E%25E5%2585%25AD%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E8%2583%25BD%25E5%25A0%25B5%25E5%25A1%259E%25E6%25BC%258F%25E6%25B4%259E-%25E5%2585%258D%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2588%2590%25E9%2581%25BF%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E5%25A0%2582%2F&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6Tdgc6rz%2Ba6PLwHdujBQ9FQE%3D&h=03788355\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E7%2599%25BD%25E9%259F%259E%25E5%2585%25AD%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E8%2583%25BD%25E5%25A0%25B5%25E5%25A1%259E%25E6%25BC%258F%25E6%25B4%259E-%25E5%2585%258D%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2588%2590%25E9%2581%25BF%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E5%25A0%2582%2F&h=3a840f86\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E7%99%BD%E9%9F%9E%E5%85%AD%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B-%E7%A8%B1%E8%83%BD%E5%A0%B5%E5%A1%9E%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E-%E5%85%8D%E6%B8%AF%E6%88%90%E9%81%BF%E7%BD%AA%E5%A4%A9%E5%A0%82/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/-IF7CtvL5jg/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F-IF7CtvL5jg%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=f62f641c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01713764c571bc0087ceb532b60391e450c2bc85","tid":1165859,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:36:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eacd660b6cbab87ee8a9fffb90a0340da1d2ce45","tid":1165859,"uid":35014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:37:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}